破Your submissions for {{ACTIVITIES}} were very similar to submissions made by another student in a previous semester. I take academic honesty very seriously and intend to pursue this apparent violation of SFU's standards for academic honesty.

As required by SFU Policy S10.02, Principles and Procedures for Academic Discipline, I am offering you the opportunity to meet with me to discuss this incident. You may wish to refer to SFU's policies and procedures on academic integrity,
